title: Number of Spotify employees 2011 to 2018
summary: In general Number of employees has rose over the Year.
Number of employees is slightly increasing from 2013 to 2014, roughly constant from 2014 to 2015, and lastly slightly increasing from 2015 to 2016.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Number of employees, of value 2162.0 was reached at Year 2016
Minimum Number of employees about 958.0 was reached at Year 2013
